  "claim_boundary": "This plan binds one MLX LoRA recipe, one MLX workflow dataset artifact, and one local snapshot publish config into the existing live adapter-cluster planner for the first swarm lane. It does not claim a second trainer runtime, full-model mixed-backend all-reduce, or automatic publication without validator, replay, and merge truth.",
